# SatTrack — Nuxt 4 Ham Radio Satellite Tracker (PWA)

## Stack
Nuxt 4 · Vue 3 `<script setup lang="ts">` · TypeScript strict · UnoCSS · IndexedDB · Custom SVG/Canvas (no mapping lib)

## Pages
| Route | File | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| `/` | `pages/index.vue` | Active pass dashboard + transponder info |
| `/pass-predict` | `pages/pass-predict.vue` | Pass list + polar plot |
| `/ar-track` | `pages/ar-track.vue` | AR compass-rotated polar plot |
| `/settings` | `pages/settings.vue` | Location · satellites · API keys · storage |

## Critical Rules
- `<script setup lang="ts">` — always, never omit `lang="ts"`
- No `any` — use `unknown` or proper types
- No `@apply` in CSS — pure UnoCSS utility classes only
- Space-Track: use `class/gp` endpoint **only** — never `tle_latest`, `tle`, or `tle_publish` (404)
- No calculations client-side — delegate everything to APIs
- GPS: timeout=30000, maximumAge=60000
- Git: `feature/* → development → main` — never skip development, never tag manually
